javax.accessibility.Accessible, java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, javax.swing.RootPaneContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.swing.WindowConstants
public class SequenceList
extends javax.swing.JFrame

SequenceList extends JFrame to display a set of sequences that the user is working on in a session. The sequence list can be stored and read back in by the application. This allows the user to usefully maintain a list of sequence that are being worked on and easily drag and drop them into sequence fields of applications.
